acceptDebt(address).details: Return whether the given goblin accepts more debt. Revert on non-goblin.

getInterestRate(uint256,uint256).details: Return the interest rate per second, using 1e18 as denom.

isGoblin(address).details: Return whether the given address is a goblin.

isOwner().details: Returns true if the caller is the current owner.

killFactor(address,uint256).details: Return the kill factor for the goblin + ETH debt, using 1e4 as denom. Revert on non-goblin.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner.     * > Note: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setGoblin(address,bool,bool,uint256,uint.details: Set the configuration for the given goblin. Must only be called by the owner.

params._acceptDebt: Whether the goblin is accepting new debts.
params._isGoblin: Whether the given address is a valid goblin.
params._killFactor: The kill factor value for this goblin.
params._workFactor: The work factor value for this goblin.
params.goblin: The goblin address to set configuration.

setParams(uint256,uint256,uint256,uint25.details: Set all the basic parameters. Must only be called by the owner.

params._interestRate: The new interest rate per second value.
params._killBps: The new reward for killing a position value.
params._minDebtSize: The new minimum debt size value.
params._reservePoolBps: The new interests allocated to the reserve pool value.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

workFactor(address,uint256).details: Return the work factor for the goblin + ETH debt, using 1e4 as denom. Revert on non-goblin.
